Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:07.99,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Wednesday Downtown! Hello everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:11.69,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Okay let's meet our first presenter, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:21.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Viking's Kotoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:29.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kotoge damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:40.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No no no, that was the worst one ever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You've done many weird things alot of times but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...this was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay everyone, this show's popular corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...the "there's someone" series, you might remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, "There's someone when you open"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the scariest thing that could happen after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's someone in the backseat" is the scariest thing that could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's someone when you wake up" is the scariest thing that could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There can't be any left though?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...always hearing "no more, no more left" but there were!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:11.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the one that I've brought this time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:19.49,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Theory : "There's someone in the bed" is the scariest thing that could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That gotta be scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely scary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All in all, this is the stuff that Hamada-san loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bit that we do just to see Hamada-san laugh his ass off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Because he loves others' misfortunes, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:42.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After this, we'll watch the "There's someone in the bed" prank loved by Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:45.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:49.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The theory that if one member of a trio leaves and you're left with the dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...you can't go on, with Jungle Pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:54.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:02:01.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We'll also search for the "bean tanks" of Japan, who are smaller than 150cm and fatter than 100 kgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:23.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory : "There's someone in the bed" is the scariest thing that could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our first target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Panzer's Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time, with help from his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:36.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we're testing the theory whilst he's alone in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And we've hidden an unknown gentleman inside his bed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.24,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Standby is OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.81,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That guy's scary as hell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ogata who returns home, suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh what the..!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS IS BULL...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh what the..!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS IS BULL...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.70,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh what the..!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS IS BULL...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:21.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He flew out of the room out of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.38,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:28.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He even ran all the way out outside of his house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:31.46,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He went outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.33,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So he went all the way out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai- Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.29,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't some kind of assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He ran outside barefooted into the snow out of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.40,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He couldn't understand anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:48.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not to have the neighbours worry too much, we head inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.31,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wah this is funny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's scary as hell man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's act.. he can stop now, its enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something like "Heyoo"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really keeping it straight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san, I think you've had alot of pranks pulled on you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...ranking those pranks by scariness what rank would this one be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's number 1!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's number 1, it made me jump and run away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:18.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As foreseen, this was clearly the scariest of them all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:23.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Amakou Inter's Seiko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.98,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh god! Oh damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:40.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She starts to change her clothes, unknowing of the weird man hiding in her house
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then on to the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.36,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to see that anyways
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,She got completely paralysed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:06.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She got paralysed altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.98,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Of course that'll happen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.82,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Haha she's completely frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.77,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I can't, this is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She can't even stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:39.75,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She went like this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My head hurts man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What show do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes a show
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A show? There are shows like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.77,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There aren't. you're right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Downtown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Downtown...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you rank this prank by scariness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no.1 of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't no damn pranks like this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you Downtown...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go somewhere quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my beloved bed ya know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got any men over yet either
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you the first man to sleep in my bed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:34.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course, it seems to be the scariest prank ever pulled on her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as funny every time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah really
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And, our next target
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Matenrou's Anthony
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:51.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shooting in his house is not allowed by his agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:57.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...so we have called him for a fake show and made him enter this hotel room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:03.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By the way, the hotel's futon is thin and a person in it would easily be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we will do the prank burying the man inside the bed itself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The man who has been part of all the "There's someone" series...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...has confirmed all theories "presented" to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...as "scariest ever"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...what will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.12,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That (hiding) guy's perseverance is amazing as well
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anthony, who felt something was off about the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,WAHH! WHAT THE-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,UWOOAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,WAHH! WHAT THE-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,UWOOAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.95,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,WAHH! WHAT THE-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,UWOOAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.10,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:08.23,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He checked one last time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.17,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What are you confirming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "How was it?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha- what's this bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's special made
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, considering all of the "there's someone" pranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...how scary was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't put them in ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:41.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since "Mr. There's someone" can't put them in ranking, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...next we have this man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Jungle Pocket's Saito
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before, he got the "There's someone when you open it"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably the scariest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...said Saito, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:02.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...will this surpass that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:09.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He checked in to a hotel before a film shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:16.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After just a minute in after the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the following happened
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.17,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.44,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What? that's quick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.36,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh the pillow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the same thing with that time? With the curtain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the "There's someone when you open it" prank
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it scarier than the previous one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,SO scary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Compared to "Someone being there when you open",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:18.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Someone being in your bed" is way scarier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And thus, it was verified to be the #1 scariest scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:31.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lastly, we test the theory with {\i1}that guy{\i0}, just in case
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.74,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Him again, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:36.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After outside sources telling us that the house was empty, we start to set up the room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.94,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They can enter so freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:45.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, since Kuro-chan carries out most of his activities on the bed, we couldn't hide the guy in his room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:54.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just for this time, we made a makeshift mattress with a hole cut out -- reverse massage table style
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:59.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Kuro-chan has finished work, and is headed to dinner by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm so hungry, it's dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mackerel and negitoro bomb! (minced tuna bowl)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Substitute rice with negitoro bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Healthy Dynamite!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.94,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's so lying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:19.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As always, Kuro-chan appeals his healthy meal. However..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:25.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After his appearance on another TV show, {\i1}Meii no THE Taikoban!*{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:41.08,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx71\fscy86\pos(466.5,232)}*Meii no THE Taikoban!{\i0} Is a Japanese medical variety TV show about celebrities' concerning health issues
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kuro-chan's blood sugar level is:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediate hospitalization-level (of seriousness)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a situation where losing consciousness and passing away is only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:44.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His blood work results were serious enough for him to be hospitalized immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:48.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Currently, he is consuming things that consist of low sugar content
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or he was supposed to be. However..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.62,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,See? I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:59.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was actually eating rice, miso soup, quail eggs, and butter-fried enoki mushrooms with his meal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Within the past 2 weeks, I've drastically changed my eating habits and health awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I pulled a fortune slip and got 'Great Blessing'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can really tell that God is watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do my best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:20.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed.. "God" is watching
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:26.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We have taken upon God and the doctor's role, and punished this liar
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, eh what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:01.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since abnormal things happening in his own house has become a normal occurrence, (from this show)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:06.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,his reaction is a little weak
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.52,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,We overdid it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In that regard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh.. what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what the heck happened to my bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:17.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Putting the bed situation aside, we move on to the diet case
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently on Taikoban, you got a harsh lecture from the doctor right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah on Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:30.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meii no THE Taikoban is airing every Monday. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,ever since his last appearance, even the doctors from the show
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:40.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,have been following Kuro-chan's lifestyle habits on Twitter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you had a very healthy meal today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't eat rice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today.. I haven't eaten rice, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not lying
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...........
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quail eggs..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice and miso soup.....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mackerel..........
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Butter-fried enoki mushrooms...............
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten those, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was my misunderstanding, then I apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a detective again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time we aired, after the show when the cameras weren't rolling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you're really in a dangerous position
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bad it's something that shouldn't be managed by you alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All the doctors (on this show) met up to talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and even then, our words did not go through you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was extremely shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're keeping your physical health in mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait..hold on a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on hold on hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lying, we're going to report to the doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't do thatー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx135\fscy153}They're so naggy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of specialist they are, but they're so naggy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our words did not go through you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was extremely shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that woman who fake cries too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:06.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, he should just die
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon further investigations, we concluded that he should just die
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's what we came to, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Seiko's bit was crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She was like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing how people can move like that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,She pulled her back and fell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She legit pulled her back and couldn't move
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't stand up when that happens, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That made my head hurt..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,from laughing so much
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-san what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's scary is that Hamada-san was like, "Those sheets are in the way"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an evil mastermind plotting was so scary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He doesn't plan on stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His evil thoughts just come out subconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to promote fear even more
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Introducing our next presenter, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Kosaka Daimaou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A pretty rare appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first appearance and I'm shaking like a new-born deer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the heck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sudden but,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was originally doing comedy in a trio
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think many people don't know this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't know you were in a trio
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I wanted to bring up something that relates to us trio comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this theory is what I brought
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:45.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Trio comedians: If one person leaves and one is useless, the duo won't last
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hmm.. I don't have experience with a trio so..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually in a trio, one or two are useless
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How was it for you guys? Did you guys all decide to break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually one by one, like Satomi Hakkenden*
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:11.18,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx47\fscy73\pos(643.5,176)}*Nanso Satomi Hakkenden{\i0} was a literary novel from the Edo period about 8 samurais that descended from dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Like 2 people remaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One by one
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like that, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:15.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Who are you going to use to verify this theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a team that is perfect for this theory
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jungle Pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:27.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Otake....It's gonna be Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean this theory is basically made for Jungle Pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If Saito-san were to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oota and Otake would remain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.27,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If Otake can last with Oota
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what we're trying to prove, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting us to ponder a little more on who's the "useless" one
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was quickly set on who is was so it shocked me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:56.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: Trio comedians - If one person leaves and one is useless, the duo won't last
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:03.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First and foremost, we begin by explaining our investigation to the two as facilitators
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.86,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh Otake is gonna be the facilitator
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,'We're going to set up the prank as "Saito-san leaving the group to become a pin-genin"*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:17.74,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx72\fscy91\pos(373.5,194)}*Pin-genin is an comedian that goes solo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the scenario, Oota-san would have to go on with Otake-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.40,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What kind of role is Otake supposed to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:23.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this case, when Saito leaves Jungle Pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:27.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,we investigate to see if Oota can continue as a duo with the "useless" Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.52,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This time he's the facilitator right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To be completely honest, continuing the duo with Otake-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is pretty rough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh..well..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it me or am I being a little disrespected here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.78,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He said it so clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well well..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask if it's rough or not...then I guess it is rough, realistically
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:53.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An uncommon prank setting where the facilitator gets his feelings hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well actually, there are a lot of times where they're on their own when I'm working alone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like during live events
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times where we work just the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oota did say that it was pretty rough when it's just the two of them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Yeah it's pretty rough when it's us two"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard that from Otake but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oota said it was pretty rough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I heard that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When something like that were to actually happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think Oota-san would continue to work with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well how should I know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I guess we'll have to see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a 50/50 chance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously have no idea what he would choose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,50/50 huh ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well well well..... 50/50 huh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:04.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In order for this prank to be realistic and efficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:12.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before the break up of the trio is announced, Saito's pin-genin wishes are going to be flaunted as shown:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:12.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx52\fscy80\pos(750,394)}Speak with other people that have experienced group break-ups
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:12.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx52\fscy80\pos(750,580)}Talk about actor aspirations during public interviews
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:12.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx52\fscy80\pos(750,744)}Saito's pin-genin wishes are revealed by other senior comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:12.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx52\fscy80\pos(750,910)}Announce break-up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, the trio break-up senior comedian -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taketo from B Course
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will start talking to Saito despite being unacquainted with him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,talking about break-ups in a sincere, intimate manner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to purposely raise suspicion about Saito leaving the group
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a live recording today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Hiruneta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hiruneta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we have a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wanted to meet a little
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much for the meal last time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no worries at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll catch you later
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to discuss things again, let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, understood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito, can I see you real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I would wonder what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he go ask for advice about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uhh, a-a-a-advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not used to being a facilitator,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the "useless" genin hardcore stutters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "If you want to discuss something again"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "If you want to discuss something again"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Advice..I don't think he would
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oota starts to question what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next step: During a fake magazine interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Saito talks about aspiring to become an actor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:39.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and how he can't let go of his passion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would be someone you aspire to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that person for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it'd be Tsutsumi Shinichi*
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:55.96,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx57\fscy80\pos(512,185)}*Tsutsumi Shinichi is a very well-known actor that has won many awards
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, you want to be an actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I originally came into this industry to become an actor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As an actor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My desire to want to progress alone is pretty strong, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to be and reality is a different story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:08.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Third step:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:11.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A senior that is close to both Oota and Saito -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Matsuoka from Chocolate Planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:17.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will reveal that Saito's wishes are leaning towards
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:20.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,wanting to be a pin-genin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.42,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was drinking with Shinji (Saito) last time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed really depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"If I decided to go on my own, what would you think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, like a pin-genin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that. So I said "what do you mean?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like "If I'm alone, then I can see it" (his future)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"What do you mean, you can see it?" I asked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that supposed to mean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but he was really pushing the subject
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, really? That sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean he's been in a lot of movies and dramas lately
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well he makes it seem like he really wants to do that kind of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The acting stuff right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was talking about some musical
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, he didn't make the cut
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were to be in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he would've been working with them for a year
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They would be on tour for a year
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, going around the world for a year or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to do something by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disturbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:19.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With 3 of these suspicious role-play
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:21.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oota begins to take notice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:23.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,of Saito's sudden odd behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At last, the main event:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:28.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Announcing the trio's break-up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:30.89,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The set-up (acting) is pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Oota decide to continue to be a due with "useless" Otake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:36.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Oota decide to continue to be a due with "useless" Otake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:43.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This day, Oota was instructed by his manager to meet at Yoshimoto's head office
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have something that needs to be discussed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito-san, if you would explain to the 2 of them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that should be discussed in our presence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that should be discussed in our presence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be frank,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to break-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and for myself to go on as a solo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what do you mean? Then, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.54,0:24:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Tokyo because
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be an actor
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.75,0:24:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fortunate to be able to be in dramas and movies
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.96,0:24:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course on top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.52,0:24:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,being able to succeed in the Owarai industry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.36,0:24:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was because of you two
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.86,0:24:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, you mean you're going to be an actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to continue to work hard as an actor
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.90,0:24:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think for myself to continue being a pin-genin
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.64,0:24:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely disrespectful to you two
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.44,0:25:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.28,0:25:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you're already in a bunch of movies and dramas
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.75,0:25:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you can still do while being a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.32,0:25:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a strong desire to work
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,alone as an actor, not a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.69,0:25:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.37,0:25:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, that's so tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is so sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.21,0:25:30.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.64,0:25:32.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Otake you don't need to add in unnecessary commentary
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.34,0:25:37.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Being thrown into this situation, Oota can't hide his shocked expression
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.75,0:25:42.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,20 minutes after, as the conversation comes to a halt,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to pursue this seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.19,0:25:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my focus to be solely on this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.59,0:25:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that means you've completely made up your mind on this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.20,0:25:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be disrespectful to you two
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.70,0:25:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring this up while I was still being indecisive
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.54,0:26:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to tell you when my mind was set
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.81,0:26:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it in another way,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought "If I don't put enough thought into this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.48,0:26:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then it would be extremely disrespectful for them"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.65,0:26:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that. He just said that himself
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.29,0:26:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.. so that's what he means
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.89,0:26:21.09,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He already said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:23.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An unexplained, unnecessary follow-up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.66,0:26:27.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, we asked Saito to leave the room for brief moment
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.76,0:26:30.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to pick their brains even more
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.37,0:26:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they believe this whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.77,0:26:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they completely understand that my decisions are pretty solid
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.95,0:26:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about Otake-san? As a fellow facilitator?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.98,0:26:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Otake is really a burden
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.92,0:26:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He is so bad at acting
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.72,0:26:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.86,0:26:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is a sudden turning point
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.86,0:26:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rough.....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going to happen to us then?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.47,0:27:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,From a business stand point, it's going to be a disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is out of the question
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.64,0:27:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jungle Pocket as an item will no longer exist
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.95,0:27:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be correct
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.78,0:27:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.59,0:27:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we tell him? (Otake to leave)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.29,0:27:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah we should really tell him soon
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.79,0:27:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he saying this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.13,0:27:32.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nothing but a burden facilitator #2
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.30,0:27:35.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was forced to leave the room
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.77,0:27:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.23,0:27:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saying irrelevant crap this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.77,0:27:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been saying he wanted to be an actor for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.45,0:27:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the right to be an obstacle in his life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.69,0:27:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that kind of person
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.92,0:28:03.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oota's manliness and courage moves Saito
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.83,0:28:07.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Although unwillingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.56,0:28:10.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oota agrees to grant Saito's wishes of breaking up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.00,0:28:14.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That being said, now we tackle the real question
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.94,0:28:14.54,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.01,0:28:17.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is really emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.27,0:28:20.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be willing to continue to work with the "useless"?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.85,0:28:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to move on with the process as a break-up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.88,0:28:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you and Otake-san would continue to work as a duo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.72,0:28:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what we were thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.59,0:28:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean continue together with Otake?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.49,0:28:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already laughing at the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.20,0:28:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oota is laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.... would people even want to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.84,0:28:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is there even a demand for that?" is too harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.67,0:28:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.24,0:28:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:54.11,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He just clicked his tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.78,0:28:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo....with Otake...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.32,0:29:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.85,0:29:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.72,0:29:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Otake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.79,0:29:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.52,0:29:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, it's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.56,0:29:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't like Otake.. it's just..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.97,0:29:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Otake.. mmm...it's..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.07,0:29:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't like Ota...ke..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is concerning him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.94,0:29:28.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It seems like he doesn't like Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.61,0:29:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pin-genin....*
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.51,0:29:34.42,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx73\fscy85\pos(372,194)}*Reminder: Pin-genin is a solo comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.22,0:29:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.09,0:29:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe pin...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.56,0:29:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I become a pin-genin, there won't be a lot of job offers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.20,0:29:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.90,0:29:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ughhhh this is so rough
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.27,0:29:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Too rough.....too rough..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.41,0:30:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, your decision to form a duo or not
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.11,0:30:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...is kind of important so I wanted to ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.98,0:30:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Going pin huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.62,0:30:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he saying he's going pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.02,0:30:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he getting closer to going pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.59,0:30:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.16,0:30:26.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,12 years ago, the three that formed a trio at NSC*
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.16,0:30:26.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx72\fscy85\pos(232.5,194)}*NSC is a comedy school
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.24,0:30:32.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They got their break thanks to Saito's personality
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.54,0:30:39.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With their ace gone, can Ota go on to form a duo with Otake?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In all honesty I believe in him
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.55,0:30:45.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.59,0:30:48.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...what will his decision be?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.96,0:30:56.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Ota decide to go on as a duo with Otake?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.53,0:31:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I mean, I kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.67,0:31:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I mean, I kind of have to do my best with Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.45,0:31:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he'll do it right, he definitely just said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.98,0:31:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.99,0:31:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it's impossible man
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.46,0:31:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd be impossible to do it alone too...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.79,0:31:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means that you'll be doing it together if I understand correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.70,0:31:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah with Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.27,0:31:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With Otake...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.51,0:31:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't sound enthusiastic about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.88,0:31:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can something be done with Otake? With me and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.08,0:31:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This does definitely not feel good
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.37,0:31:46.67,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Of course you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.82,0:31:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.09,0:31:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.89,0:31:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...We don't have to go on forever right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.02,0:31:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell, he is already thinking of breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.36,0:32:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Again he doesn't sound excited, what's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean there's nothing to do but do my best with Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.47,0:32:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.10,0:32:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, this means we're moving forward with you and Otake as a duo
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.71,0:32:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.85,0:32:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As a duo right? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.68,0:32:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.12,0:32:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.89,0:32:25.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After nearly worrying himself to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.32,0:32:30.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ota has decided to form a duo with the useless Otake
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.96,0:32:32.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That means
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:35.17,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're revealing the prank
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Ota~~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn man...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.40,0:32:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You really got worried didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.78,0:32:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You really were thinking about it, Ota
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.31,0:32:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold up. Is being in a duo with me that unappealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.05,0:32:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were really worried, sorry man
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.02,0:32:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.86,0:33:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is freaking bullshit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.26,0:33:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh this is so strange
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.69,0:33:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That really pisses me off
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.16,0:33:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, I'm telling you you're acting weird-
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.90,0:33:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but I'm the one that's gotten hurt the most from this situation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.47,0:33:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the one that got hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.70,0:33:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx96\fscy118}NO ONE GIVES A SHIT ABOUT YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.94,0:33:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not the one getting attacked all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.10,0:33:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.17,0:33:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an agenda isn't there. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.58,0:33:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Wednesday Downtown...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.71,0:33:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This was to test the theory that if you take one out of a trio and leave the person with the useless member
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.81,0:33:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't go on to form a duo
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.52,0:33:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we say that you will go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.82,0:33:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...that's one weird theory
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.73,0:33:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I still haven't agreed to that theory
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.36,0:33:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "Can he come together with the junk guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.97,0:33:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really gonna shine light on that real of a part of human nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.44,0:33:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean, if you think about widening the possibilities from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.81,0:33:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have to think about leaving Otake behind as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.95,0:34:03.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That means, even if it is with a useless person, you form a duo for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.76,0:34:06.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He REALLY thought about it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it came to continuing together. What do you think about it Nicole?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.22,0:34:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of got teary eyed at his agony
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.33,0:34:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god there's Saito-san with them
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good that they're a trio like that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.25,0:34:23.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Now let's have them come out please!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.61,0:34:24.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh they're here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.51,0:34:38.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Ota and Otake!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.96,0:34:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a preschooler kind of mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.20,0:34:47.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hold up, you can't even turn and come out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.16,0:34:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't know how it was setup
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.50,0:34:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how the footing was set
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The step yes, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.47,0:34:57.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ota really went like uhhngh
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.15,0:35:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The real worry was that Saito was going away
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.08,0:35:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real though, even today...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.05,0:35:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,....Saito isn't here right...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.80,0:35:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at the Budokan*
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.80,0:35:11.52,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx72\fscy95\pos(274.5,192)}*Budokan is a big concert hall
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.12,0:35:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's gone because of some musical related work he's doing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.00,0:35:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In that situation when he tells you he wants to become an actor alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.42,0:35:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...isn't it super real?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.89,0:35:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There was alot of pre setup
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.90,0:35:19.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Lots of setup
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.83,0:35:23.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Otake your feelings must've been really weird right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.50,0:35:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This segment was really hard on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.28,0:35:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm kind of an accomplice to it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.51,0:35:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not really fully an accomplice either
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.93,0:35:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave me alot of bad info about what Ota thinks of me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.58,0:35:42.69,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Don't talk for so long, I'll end up laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:44.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Don't talk for too long, it's enough
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.69,0:35:47.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If he goes on too long, you'll laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.22,0:35:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out a bit though
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.37,0:35:53.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Let's do a prank where Otake has to leave the trio
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.20,0:35:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen probably
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.13,0:36:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,, We've been a trio for about 12 years and 4 times we've thought about kicking him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.16,0:36:05.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next we have the corner where we bring you theories from around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.48,0:36:08.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Viewers' Theory Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.03,0:36:10.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenters are...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.78,0:36:16.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Daian
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in your care
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.68,0:36:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been about half a year
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.68,0:36:20.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Your second time right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.82,0:36:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it's our second time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.93,0:36:23.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eeh~ I thought it was your first
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.17,0:36:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we have any impact on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.12,0:36:28.09,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.65,0:36:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We would've stated it more if it were the case
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.12,0:36:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been told that we look alike but have no blood relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.31,0:36:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move along then, the theory that we've brought you today is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.66,0:36:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Theory: We can find Mame Tanks with a height under 150cm and weight over 100kg...*
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.66,0:36:47.98,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fscx62\fscy85\pos(676.5,64)}*Mame tank refers to disproportionate body types with overweight body, and short height
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.72,0:36:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...if we were to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.80,0:36:56.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Mame Tank huh? That's a word I haven't heard in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.27,0:36:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that you can find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:37:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...while going around the city
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Osaka has an image of having these types of people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.19,0:37:06.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That means that there are alot of them in Osaka right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.04,0:37:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to some downtown shopping street most of the people there are like that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.94,0:37:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.87,0:37:12.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So that means the theory is proven
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.51,0:37:15.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We don't need it, they're not even rare then
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.47,0:37:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There actually weren't that many
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.81,0:37:20.91,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Pick one for god's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.91,0:37:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality there weren't many of them
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.62,0:37:25.99,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It feels like..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.44,0:37:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like they are but actually aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.16,0:37:47.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We're testing the theory that we can find Mame Tanks with a height under 150cm and weight over 100kg if we go out to look for them
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.92,0:37:51.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, let's start our investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.75,0:37:53.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.70,0:37:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with a program called Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.90,0:37:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.57,0:38:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.30,0:38:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it's ok yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.65,0:38:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we shoot your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.66,0:38:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is looking for me so it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.22,0:38:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just behind there
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.46,0:38:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeees yes yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.57,0:38:16.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He accepted the interview with a high-pitched voice but...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.07,0:38:23.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We weren't allowed to put out numbers concerning his weight and height
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.70,0:38:25.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.22,0:38:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please share you weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.14,0:38:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no- It's kinda difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.60,0:38:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No waay- that's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.47,0:38:37.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of a complex about their physique
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.62,0:38:42.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We're not finding anyone who would let us show their face, let alone share their measurements
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.60,0:38:44.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That means
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.67,0:38:49.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stopping the search in the streets, we go to the net to find them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.52,0:38:54.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We try to get our hands on anyone who might be like that..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.00,0:39:01.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first one, working at a maid cafe called "MuchiPocha"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.87,0:39:08.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro Kokoa with a height of 157cm and a weight of 120kg
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.32,0:39:16.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wasn't under 150cm but she was a complete Mame Tank, when we talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.45,0:39:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,About when did you start putting on weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.77,0:39:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only about 47kg in high school but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.07,0:39:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...after my graduation, I stopped doing sports and in the blink of an eye I became three times my old weight
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.87,0:39:35.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next we have Ihashi Gouta from DDT Pro Wrestling
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.92,0:39:43.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has a special body with 158cm in height and 136kg in weight, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.72,0:39:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this physique a disadvantage for pro wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.07,0:39:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, of course being tall is better but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.07,0:39:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...doing a Moon salto and other similar flip-style moves is easier
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.00,0:40:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things that I can only do because I'm small
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.34,0:40:04.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And there's this person working at this bar
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.80,0:40:11.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Looks like a nice place
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.45,0:40:08.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Named "Japan Worldwide Debusu Club"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.79,0:40:13.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Height 163 cm, weight 120 kg
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.24,0:40:15.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Louis Vuitton
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.79,0:40:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just walking around
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.76,0:40:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll receive a whole large pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A random person gives it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.20,0:40:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a complete stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.64,0:40:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They just give me items that they have on them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.36,0:40:28.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Additionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.21,0:40:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With gaining that much weight
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.99,0:40:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,does it affect your health in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.39,0:40:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get my physical exam, my blood glucose level is normal
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.15,0:40:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A physician once performed an exam on me, and said I'm a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.32,0:40:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever get a nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.73,0:40:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.44,0:40:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been called "Mame Tank" or "Fatty than can move"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.46,0:40:51.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We found someone that was nicknamed "Mame Tank"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.50,0:40:54.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, didn't fit the criteria of being under 150 cm, and over 100 kg
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.98,0:41:00.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We struggle to find the person that fits the mame tank appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.65,0:41:04.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, in that bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.21,0:41:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind telling us your height and weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.98,0:41:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm at 148 cm, 110 kg
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.50,0:41:16.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There she is; mame tank
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.23,0:41:18.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, her weight used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.21,0:41:21.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,90kg about a month ago
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.37,0:41:25.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She says she quickly gained 10 kg within that month
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.62,0:41:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you gain so much weight in a span of one month?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.20,0:41:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of rice
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.76,0:41:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I've been eating 3 cups per meal, I eat at least 10 cups per day
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.56,0:41:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My height is 150 cm
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.26,0:41:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weight is probably 115 kg or more
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.16,0:41:47.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having her 3-size (bust, waist, hip) all be 140 cm,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.59,0:41:51.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she'll be categorized as the cylindrical body type
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.21,0:41:56.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Height 145 cm, weight 101 kg,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.96,0:42:02.96,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is.....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.05,0:42:00.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she's the super tiny mame tank
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.21,0:42:04.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As suspected, the mame tank body type that fits
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:09.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,our criteria exists here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.26,0:42:13.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Further more, we found someone that wasn't under 150 cm,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.01,0:42:17.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but had the highest BMI index
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.87,0:42:22.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During this investigation, we found an extreme mame tank
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.13,0:42:25.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is that person
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.09,0:42:35.08,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She's injured
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.92,0:42:36.01,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She looks really injured
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.44,0:42:37.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Osaka's chubby Cabaret King
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.94,0:42:39.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Takenokonosato-body type
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.80,0:42:42.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kitty-san
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.48,0:42:44.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her weight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.72,0:42:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How many kg?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.05,0:42:53.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With the same exact height as Watanabe Naomi
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.75,0:42:56.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But weights 60 kg more
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.67,0:42:58.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An extreme body
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.68,0:43:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.81,0:43:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell from the stairs in the store
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.89,0:43:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.74,0:43:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to get an MRI
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.71,0:43:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but was told that my body is too big
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.22,0:43:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you didn't fit inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.95,0:43:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't fit in the machine so it wouldn't move
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.40,0:43:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because of my weight
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.81,0:43:24.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On top of that, was unable to fit in a wheelchair
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.54,0:43:27.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and unable to use crutches as support
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.19,0:43:30.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She really worries the doctors -- even more than Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.72,0:43:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stopped like {\i1}this{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.23,0:43:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and was like "this is going to be a little difficult.."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.83,0:43:40.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.35,0:43:45.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People with mame tank bodies, please be careful of your physical health
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.62,0:43:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.15,0:43:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there were a few (mame tanks to be found)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.07,0:43:53.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah........
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.16,0:44:02.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Up next week: Theory - Buy 10,000 Yen worth of items to keep you warm
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.30,0:44:07.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and compete in an endurance game in -15° C weather
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.16,0:44:12.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, Top animal playground equipment ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:19.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And, Theory: In a "You're the one who's going to sing?!" situation, would you be able to tsukkomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.12,0:44:22.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory verification involving Hamada as well!
